//// OBB 이용하여 무게중심이 Form closure 형태로 산출되면 Monment 산출하여 net moment가 일정 이하면 안정적인 접촉으로 간주함.
bool TEMPLATE_MATCHING::findMultipleContactPoint2(CTARGET_OBJECT_DATA* &target_object_data)
{
    bool is_stable_contact = false;
    m_math.extractCloud(*target_object_data->cloud_process_object_CAD_simulation, *target_object_data->simulation_collision_idx_cloud_in, *target_object_data->collision_cloud_in);
    m_math.extractCloud(*target_object_data->cloud_simulation_merged_object_with_bin, *target_object_data->simulation_collision_idx_cloud_map, *target_object_data->collision_cloud_map);

    ///////////////////////////////////////////////
    //// a) Penetration check
    // Nearest point to bin
    //// FIXME: 아래 z 최소값 구해서 마지막에 bin 바닥과 접촉하도록 미세한 translation 필요  - 복셀 특성 상 약간 떠있음
    pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZ>::Ptr collision_cloud_in_xyz(new pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZ>);
    pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZ>::Ptr collision_cloud_map_xyz(new pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZ>);
    pcl::copyPointCloud(*target_object_data->collision_cloud_in, *collision_cloud_in_xyz);
    pcl::copyPointCloud(*target_object_data->collision_cloud_map, *collision_cloud_map_xyz);
    pcl::PointXYZ minPt_in, maxPt_in, minPt_map, maxPt_map;
    m_math.genCloudMinMax(*collision_cloud_in_xyz, minPt_in, maxPt_in);
    m_math.genCloudMinMax(*collision_cloud_map_xyz, minPt_map, maxPt_map);

    //// HERE: 아래 부분이 수행되어야 뚫고 들어가지 않음
    // Penetration만큼 위로 상승
    float bin_plane_z = 15.0;
    // float dist_object_to_bin = minPt_in.z - bin_plane_z;
    float dist_object_to_bin = minPt_in.z - maxPt_map.z;
    float thre_dist = 1.0; // if the object is penetrated.
    if(dist_object_to_bin < thre_dist)
    {
        //// TODO::연산량 측면에서는 아래 부분은 삭제할 필요
        //// 점유 여부 다시 확인
        if(1) 
        {
            // printf("Re-check collision!\n");
            // RVIZ visualizing 문제
            extractCollisionCloudResultsWithKDTree(target_object_data, "r", *target_object_data->cloud_process_object_CAD_simulation);
            //// 충돌 cloud 다시 추출
            m_math.extractCloud(*target_object_data->cloud_process_object_CAD_simulation, *target_object_data->simulation_collision_idx_cloud_in, *target_object_data->collision_cloud_in);
            m_math.extractCloud(*target_object_data->cloud_simulation_merged_object_with_bin, *target_object_data->simulation_collision_idx_cloud_map, *target_object_data->collision_cloud_map);
        }
    }

    ///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
    ///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
    ///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
    
    Eigen::Vector3f obj_com_pt = target_object_data->simulation_center_of_mass_process;
    if(0) //// 접촉 점군의 중심점 이용
    {
        //// b) Contact motion 생성 - 중력 고려
        //// FIXME: 아래는 center를 선택한 것, 추후 최초 접촉점을 선택하도록 변경하기
        Eigen::Vector3f query_pt, query_normal;
        int idx_in, idx_map;
        m_pcl_proc.extractCenterWithNormal(*target_object_data->collision_cloud_in, query_pt, query_normal, idx_in);
        m_pcl_proc.extractCenterWithNormal(*target_object_data->collision_cloud_map, query_pt, query_normal, idx_map);
        size_t idx_in_center = target_object_data->simulation_collision_idx_cloud_in->indices[idx_in];
        size_t idx_map_center = target_object_data->simulation_collision_idx_cloud_map->indices[idx_map];

        Eigen::VectorXf contact_pt_normal_in(6);
        contact_pt_normal_in.segment<3>(0) = target_object_data->cloud_process_object_CAD_simulation->points[idx_in_center].getVector3fMap();
        contact_pt_normal_in.segment<3>(3) = target_object_data->cloud_process_object_CAD_simulation->points[idx_in_center].getNormalVector3fMap();

        Eigen::VectorXf contact_pt_normal_map(6);
        // contact_pt_normal_map.segment<3>(0) = target_object_data->cloud_bin_CAD_uniformly_downsampled_bin_frame_with_normal->points[idx_map_center].getVector3fMap();
        // contact_pt_normal_map.segment<3>(3) = target_object_data->cloud_bin_CAD_uniformly_downsampled_bin_frame_with_normal->points[idx_map_center].getNormalVector3fMap();
        contact_pt_normal_map.segment<3>(0) = target_object_data->cloud_simulation_merged_object_with_bin->points[idx_map_center].getVector3fMap();
        contact_pt_normal_map.segment<3>(3) = target_object_data->cloud_simulation_merged_object_with_bin->points[idx_map_center].getNormalVector3fMap();

        //// *target_object_data->cloud_process_object_CAD_simulation는 bin frame 기준으로 변환된 cloud
        // m_math.printVector(contact_pt_normal_in, "contact_pt_normal_in");
        // m_math.printVector(contact_pt_normal_map, "contact_pt_normal_map");

        //// c) 접촉점으로부터 물체의 중심점으로의 방향벡터 산출
        Eigen::Vector3f contact_pt = contact_pt_normal_in.segment<3>(0);
        Eigen::Vector3f direction_com2contact = contact_pt - obj_com_pt;
        // m_math.printVector3f(direction_com2contact, "direction_com2contact");

        // Contact normal은 상자의 접촉점의 CAD normal
        //// TODO: CAD의 normal이 90도 꺾이는 곳에서 다를 수 있으므로, 근처 점 여러개를 이용하여 평균 법선을 구하도록 처리하기.
        Eigen::Vector3f contact_normal = -contact_pt_normal_map.segment<3>(3); // 물체 A 입장에서 A의 외부를 향하는 방향벡터
        target_object_data->r_vector_com2contact = direction_com2contact;
        target_object_data->contact_pt = contact_pt;
        target_object_data->contact_normal = contact_normal;
        // m_math.printVector3f(contact_normal, "contact_normal");

        // Vector from contact point to COM
        target_object_data->simulation_object.setRelativePosition(target_object_data->r_vector_com2contact);
        target_object_data->simulation_object.setContactPoint(target_object_data->contact_pt);
        target_object_data->simulation_object.setContactNormal(target_object_data->contact_normal);


        ////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
        ////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
        ///////////// isContactStable 함수 내에서 사용, 하지만 이 함수 아직 사용안함 ///////////
        ////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
        ////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
                //// d) 접촉점 주위의 일정 반경 내의 점군 저장 (접촉 안정성에 사용)
                std::vector<int> vec_idx_contact_nearest;
                std::vector<float> vec_dist_contact_nearest;
                float radius_contact_nearest = 5.0;
                pcl::PointIndices::Ptr idx_contact_nearest(new pcl::PointIndices());

                Eigen::Vector4f search_query_pt(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 1.0);
                search_query_pt.segment<3>(0) = contact_pt;
                search_query_pt = target_object_data->T_process_simulation.inverse()*search_query_pt;
                Eigen::Vector3f contact_pt_object_frame = search_query_pt.segment<3>(0);
                // m_math.printVector3f(contact_pt_object_frame, "contact_pt_object_frame");
                m_math.findRadiusNearestIndex(target_object_data->md_KdTree_octoMap_CAD, contact_pt_object_frame, vec_idx_contact_nearest, vec_dist_contact_nearest, radius_contact_nearest);
                m_math.vec2Indices(vec_idx_contact_nearest, *idx_contact_nearest);

                ////////////////////////////
                //// nearest cloud save
                pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZRGBNormal>::Ptr cloud_contact_nearest(new pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZRGBNormal>);
                m_math.extractCloud(*target_object_data->cloud_process_object_CAD_simulation, *idx_contact_nearest, *cloud_contact_nearest);
                // RGB allocation
                printf("cloud_contact_nearest->size() : %zu\n", cloud_contact_nearest->size());
                for (size_t i = 0; i < cloud_contact_nearest->size(); i++)
                {
                    cloud_contact_nearest->points[i].r = 255.0;
                    cloud_contact_nearest->points[i].g = 127.0;
                    cloud_contact_nearest->points[i].b = 0.0;
                }
                // target_object_data->m_set_cloud_contact_nearest.push_back(*cloud_contact_nearest);
                ////////////////////////////

                target_object_data->m_set_idx_contact_nearest.push_back(*idx_contact_nearest); // 선택된 center 주위의 radius search 결과인 cloud의 인덱스
                target_object_data->idx_set_contact_point.push_back(idx_in_center); // 선택된 center의 raw 인덱스
        ////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
        ////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
        ////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
        ////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
        ////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

        //// FIXME: for문 밖으로 아래 update 부분을 빼서, 안정도 판별 부분과 연동
        //// 회전 중심 기준 좌표계 update
        // update
        Eigen::Matrix4f T_bin2Contact = Eigen::Matrix4f::Identity();

        Eigen::Vector3f direction_major_axis = direction_com2contact;
        direction_major_axis.normalize();
        Eigen::Vector3f direction_rotation_axis = contact_normal.cross(direction_major_axis);
        direction_rotation_axis.normalize();
        Eigen::Vector3f direction_sub_axis = direction_major_axis.cross(direction_rotation_axis);
        direction_sub_axis.normalize();

        T_bin2Contact.block<3, 1>(0, 0) = direction_sub_axis; // rotation vec_x
        T_bin2Contact.block<3, 1>(0, 1) = direction_rotation_axis; // rotation vec_y
        T_bin2Contact.block<3, 1>(0, 2) = direction_major_axis; // rotation vec_z

        //// 일단 무게중심을 기준으로 동작하도록 설정
        if(0) T_bin2Contact.block<3, 1>(0, 3) = contact_pt; // Contact point
        else T_bin2Contact.block<3, 1>(0, 3) = obj_com_pt; // COM
        

        target_object_data->T_bin2Contact = T_bin2Contact;
        target_object_data->T_contact2Bin = T_bin2Contact.inverse();

    }
    else // 모든 접촉 점군의 모멘트 계산
    {

        Eigen::MatrixXf contact_pt_set(target_object_data->collision_cloud_in->size(), 3);
        Eigen::MatrixXf contact_normal_set(target_object_data->collision_cloud_in->size(), 3);
        Eigen::MatrixXf direction_com2contact_set(target_object_data->collision_cloud_in->size(), 3);
        int idx_in, idx_map;
        Eigen::Vector3f contact_pt_A, contact_pt_B, contact_normal_B;
        for (size_t i = 0; i < direction_com2contact_set.rows(); i++)
        {
            contact_pt_A = target_object_data->collision_cloud_in->points[i].getVector3fMap();
            m_pcl_proc.extractNearestPointWithNormal(contact_pt_A, *target_object_data->collision_cloud_map, contact_pt_B, contact_normal_B, idx_in);
            contact_pt_set.row(i) = contact_pt_A;            
            contact_normal_set.row(i) = -contact_normal_B; // 물체 A 입장에서 A의 외부를 향하는 방향벡터
            direction_com2contact_set.row(i) =  contact_pt_A - obj_com_pt;
        }
        // std::cout << "direction_com2contact_set - " << direction_com2contact_set.rows() << ", " << direction_com2contact_set.cols() << " (rows, cols)" << std::endl;
        // std::cout << "direction_com2contact_set: " << direction_com2contact_set << std::endl;
        
        target_object_data->simulation_object.setRelativePositionSet(direction_com2contact_set);
        target_object_data->simulation_object.setContactPointSet(contact_pt_set);
        target_object_data->simulation_object.setContactNormalSet(contact_normal_set);



        ////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
        // Eigen::Vector3f query_pt, query_normal;
        // m_pcl_proc.extractCenterWithNormal(*target_object_data->collision_cloud_in, query_pt, query_normal, idx_in);
        // m_pcl_proc.extractCenterWithNormal(*target_object_data->collision_cloud_map, query_pt, query_normal, idx_map);
        // size_t idx_in_center = target_object_data->simulation_collision_idx_cloud_in->indices[idx_in];
        // size_t idx_map_center = target_object_data->simulation_collision_idx_cloud_map->indices[idx_map];
        // Eigen::VectorXf contact_pt_normal_in(6);
        // contact_pt_normal_in.segment<3>(0) = target_object_data->cloud_process_object_CAD_simulation->points[idx_in_center].getVector3fMap();
        // contact_pt_normal_in.segment<3>(3) = target_object_data->cloud_process_object_CAD_simulation->points[idx_in_center].getNormalVector3fMap();
        // Eigen::VectorXf contact_pt_normal_map(6);
        // contact_pt_normal_map.segment<3>(0) = target_object_data->cloud_simulation_merged_object_with_bin->points[idx_map_center].getVector3fMap();
        // contact_pt_normal_map.segment<3>(3) = target_object_data->cloud_simulation_merged_object_with_bin->points[idx_map_center].getNormalVector3fMap();
        // //// c) 접촉점으로부터 물체의 중심점으로의 방향벡터 산출
        // Eigen::Vector3f contact_pt = contact_pt_normal_in.segment<3>(0);
        // Eigen::Vector3f direction_com2contact = contact_pt - obj_com_pt;
        // Eigen::Vector3f contact_normal = -contact_pt_normal_map.segment<3>(3); // 물체 A 입장에서 A의 외부를 향하는 방향벡터
        // target_object_data->r_vector_com2contact = direction_com2contact;
        // target_object_data->contact_pt = contact_pt;
        // target_object_data->contact_normal = contact_normal;
        // // Vector from contact point to COM
        // target_object_data->simulation_object.setRelativePosition(target_object_data->r_vector_com2contact);
        // target_object_data->simulation_object.setContactPoint(target_object_data->contact_pt);
        // target_object_data->simulation_object.setContactNormal(target_object_data->contact_normal);




        ////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
        ////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
        ///////////// isContactStable 함수 내에서 사용, 하지만 이 함수 아직 사용안함 ///////////
        ////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
        ////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
                // //// d) 접촉점 주위의 일정 반경 내의 점군 저장 (접촉 안정성에 사용)
                // std::vector<int> vec_idx_contact_nearest;
                // std::vector<float> vec_dist_contact_nearest;
                // float radius_contact_nearest = 5.0;
                // pcl::PointIndices::Ptr idx_contact_nearest(new pcl::PointIndices());

                // Eigen::Vector4f search_query_pt(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 1.0);
                // search_query_pt.segment<3>(0) = contact_pt;
                // search_query_pt = target_object_data->T_process_simulation.inverse()*search_query_pt;
                // Eigen::Vector3f contact_pt_object_frame = search_query_pt.segment<3>(0);
                // // m_math.printVector3f(contact_pt_object_frame, "contact_pt_object_frame");
                // m_math.findRadiusNearestIndex(target_object_data->md_KdTree_octoMap_CAD, contact_pt_object_frame, vec_idx_contact_nearest, vec_dist_contact_nearest, radius_contact_nearest);
                // m_math.vec2Indices(vec_idx_contact_nearest, *idx_contact_nearest);

                // ////////////////////////////
                // //// nearest cloud save
                // pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZRGBNormal>::Ptr cloud_contact_nearest(new pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZRGBNormal>);
                // m_math.extractCloud(*target_object_data->cloud_process_object_CAD_simulation, *idx_contact_nearest, *cloud_contact_nearest);
                // // RGB allocation
                // printf("cloud_contact_nearest->size() : %zu\n", cloud_contact_nearest->size());
                // for (size_t i = 0; i < cloud_contact_nearest->size(); i++)
                // {
                //     cloud_contact_nearest->points[i].r = 255.0;
                //     cloud_contact_nearest->points[i].g = 127.0;
                //     cloud_contact_nearest->points[i].b = 0.0;
                // }
                // // target_object_data->m_set_cloud_contact_nearest.push_back(*cloud_contact_nearest);
                // ////////////////////////////

                // target_object_data->m_set_idx_contact_nearest.push_back(*idx_contact_nearest); // 선택된 center 주위의 radius search 결과인 cloud의 인덱스
                // target_object_data->idx_set_contact_point.push_back(idx_in_center); // 선택된 center의 raw 인덱스
        ////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
        ////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
        ////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
        ////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
        ////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
       
    }


    //// CODEHERE: 여기에 현재 안정도 판별 삼각형?, OBB?
    //// FIXME: 
    //// TODO: 첫 접촉이면 상관없지만, 다중 접촉에서는 어느 점을 중심으로 회전할지를 결정해야 함.
    //// TODO: *cloud_contact_nearest_merged를 xy평면에 정사영 후,  xy평면에 정사영한 COM이 박스 내에 포함되어 있으면 안정으로 판단
    pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZRGBNormal>::Ptr cloud_contact_nearest_merged(new pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZRGBNormal>);
    pcl::copyPointCloud(*target_object_data->collision_cloud_in, *cloud_contact_nearest_merged);
    if(isPointInsideOBB(*cloud_contact_nearest_merged, obj_com_pt, false))
    {
        //// TODO: COM과 추출된 Bounding box 내의 점들 사이의 모멘트를 계산하여 합 모멘트가 0에 근접한 경우를 안정한 경우로 판별
        Eigen::Vector3f net_moment; // Mx, My, Mz

        // 다시 object frame으로 변환
        Eigen::Matrix4f T_O2Process = target_object_data->T_process_simulation.inverse(); 
        pcl::transformPointCloudWithNormals(*cloud_contact_nearest_merged, *cloud_contact_nearest_merged, T_O2Process);
        calNetMoment(*cloud_contact_nearest_merged, target_object_data->simulation_center_of_mass_object_frame.segment<3>(0), net_moment); // object frame
        
        printf("\n\n7777777777777777777777777777777\n");
        printf("7777777777777777777777777777777\n\n");
        m_math.printVector3f(net_moment, "net_moment");
        printf("\n7777777777777777777777777777777\n\n");
        printf("7777777777777777777777777777777\n");

        //// FIXME: 아래 값을 어떻게 정의하느냐에 따라 수렴 결과가 달라짐
        //// TODO: 수렴 지점 근처에서 motion의 변위를 점점 줄여가도록 weight 도입
        // 약 30~40
        float thre_net_moment = 45.0;
        if(fabs(net_moment[0]) < thre_net_moment && fabs(net_moment[1]) < thre_net_moment && fabs(net_moment[2]) < thre_net_moment)
        {
            is_stable_contact = true;
        }
    }
    return is_stable_contact;
}

bool TEMPLATE_MATCHING::isContactStable(CTARGET_OBJECT_DATA* &target_object_data)
{
    pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZRGBNormal>::Ptr cloud_contact_nearest(new pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZRGBNormal>);
    for (size_t i = 0; i < target_object_data->m_set_idx_contact_nearest.size(); i++)
    {
        //// NOTICE: CAD object 좌표계 기준 추출하면 좌표계가 달라지므로, 그대로 process bin 좌표계 이용
        pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZRGBNormal>::Ptr cloud_tmp(new pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZRGBNormal>);
        m_math.extractCloud(*target_object_data->cloud_process_object_CAD_simulation, target_object_data->m_set_idx_contact_nearest[i], *cloud_tmp);
        *cloud_contact_nearest += *cloud_tmp;
    }


    //// NOTICE: 아래 아직 구현 안되어 있음
    //// TODO: 무게중심이 접촉점의 span 안에 있는지 확인
	// combination of segment idx
	std::vector<std::vector<size_t>> idx_set_triangle_vertics;
	idx_set_triangle_vertics = m_math.combnk(target_object_data->idx_set_contact_point, 3); // 점 3개를 뽑아서 삼각형 생성
    printf("idx_set_triangle_vertics size: %zu\n", idx_set_triangle_vertics.size());
    for (size_t i = 0; i < idx_set_triangle_vertics.size(); i++)
    {
        printf("\n*******************************\n");
        std::vector<size_t> triangle_vertics = idx_set_triangle_vertics[i];
        Eigen::Vector3f pt_1 = target_object_data->cloud_process_object_CAD_simulation->points[triangle_vertics[0]].getVector3fMap();
        Eigen::Vector3f pt_2 = target_object_data->cloud_process_object_CAD_simulation->points[triangle_vertics[1]].getVector3fMap();
        Eigen::Vector3f pt_3 = target_object_data->cloud_process_object_CAD_simulation->points[triangle_vertics[2]].getVector3fMap();
        m_math.printVector3f(pt_1, "pt_1");
        m_math.printVector3f(pt_2, "pt_2");
        m_math.printVector3f(pt_3, "pt_3");
        printf("*******************************\n");

    }
    

    //// 그냥 접촉점에서의 힘/토크 계산해서 합해서 moment가 발생하면 회전하도록 처리하기

    // 접촉점과 접촉영역 cloud idx 초기화
    target_object_data->idx_set_contact_point.clear();
    target_object_data->m_set_idx_contact_nearest.clear();
    // target_object_data->m_set_cloud_contact_nearest.clear();


    float norm_tmp = (target_object_data->simulation_center_of_mass_process - target_object_data->simulation_center_of_mass_process_before).norm();
    float thre_dist_simulation_contact_stable = 3.0; // 3mm 이내
    if(norm_tmp < thre_dist_simulation_contact_stable) target_object_data->simulation_contact_stable_cnt++;
    else target_object_data->simulation_contact_stable_cnt = 0;


    // printf("Dist norm: %0.2f, Contact stable count: %zu\n", norm_tmp, target_object_data->simulation_contact_stable_cnt);


    return false;
}

bool TEMPLATE_MATCHING::isPointInsideOBB(const pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZRGBNormal> &cloud_in, const Eigen::Vector3f &query_point, bool b_plot)
{
    printf("*********************************isPointInsideOBB!!!\n\n");
    printf("*********************************isPointInsideOBB!!!\n\n");
    bool is_point_inside_obb = false;
    //// OBB (Object-oriented Bounding Box)
    // Compute principal directions
    pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZRGBNormal>::Ptr cloudPlaneProjected (new pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZRGBNormal>);
    pcl::copyPointCloud(cloud_in, *cloudPlaneProjected);

    //// XY plane
    for (size_t i = 0; i < cloudPlaneProjected->size(); i++) cloudPlaneProjected->points[i].z = 0.0;
    Eigen::Vector3f query_point_raw = query_point;
    Eigen::Vector3f query_point_xy_plane = query_point;
    query_point_xy_plane[2] = 0.0;
    ////

    Eigen::Vector4f pcaCentroid;
    pcl::compute3DCentroid(*cloudPlaneProjected, pcaCentroid);
    Eigen::Matrix3f covariance;
    computeCovarianceMatrixNormalized(*cloudPlaneProjected, pcaCentroid, covariance);
    Eigen::SelfAdjointEigenSolver<Eigen::Matrix3f> eigen_solver(covariance, Eigen::ComputeEigenvectors);
    Eigen::Matrix3f eigenVectorsPCA = eigen_solver.eigenvectors();
    eigenVectorsPCA.col(2) = eigenVectorsPCA.col(0).cross(eigenVectorsPCA.col(1));  /// This line is necessary for proper orientation in some cases. The numbers come out the same without it, but

    // Transform the original cloud to the origin where the principal components correspond to the axes.
    Eigen::Matrix4f projectionTransform(Eigen::Matrix4f::Identity());
    projectionTransform.block<3,3>(0,0) = eigenVectorsPCA.transpose();
    projectionTransform.block<3,1>(0,3) = -1.f * (projectionTransform.block<3,3>(0,0) * pcaCentroid.head<3>());
    pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZRGBNormal>::Ptr cloudPointsProjected (new pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZRGBNormal>);
    pcl::transformPointCloudWithNormals(*cloudPlaneProjected, *cloudPointsProjected, projectionTransform);

    // Get the minimum and maximum points of the transformed cloud.
    pcl::PointXYZRGBNormal minPoint, maxPoint;
    pcl::getMinMax3D(*cloudPointsProjected, minPoint, maxPoint);
    const Eigen::Vector3f meanDiagonal = 0.5f*(maxPoint.getVector3fMap() + minPoint.getVector3fMap());

    // Final transform
    const Eigen::Quaternionf bboxQuaternion(eigenVectorsPCA); //Quaternions are a way to do rotations https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mHVwd8gYLnI
    const Eigen::Vector3f bboxTransform = eigenVectorsPCA * meanDiagonal + pcaCentroid.head<3>();

    Eigen::Vector3f box_dim;
    box_dim = maxPoint.getVector3fMap() - minPoint.getVector3fMap();
    // printf("Box dimension: %0.3f, %0.3f, %0.3f\n", box_dim[0], box_dim[1], box_dim[2]);

    std::vector<double> box_dim_list(3);
    for (int k = 0; k < 3; k++) { box_dim_list[k] = box_dim[k]; }
    std::vector<double> box_dim_sorted_list;
    std::vector<size_t> box_dim_sorted_idx_list;
    m_math.genAscendingOrder(box_dim_list, box_dim_sorted_list, box_dim_sorted_idx_list);


    ////
    // Input point
    Eigen::Vector4f query_point_obb(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 1.0);
    query_point_obb.segment<3>(0) = query_point_xy_plane;
    query_point_obb = projectionTransform*query_point_obb;

    // Bounding box
    std::vector<double> bb_box = {minPoint.x, maxPoint.x, minPoint.y, maxPoint.y, minPoint.z, maxPoint.z};
    Eigen::Vector3f bb_box_length(maxPoint.x - minPoint.x, maxPoint.y - minPoint.y, maxPoint.z - minPoint.z);
    // m_math.printVector(bb_box, "OBB bb_box");
    // m_math.printVector3f(bb_box_length, "bb_box_length");
    // m_math.printVector3f(query_point_obb.segment<3>(0), "query_point_obb");
    bool is_pt_in_x_range = minPoint.x <= query_point_obb[0] && query_point_obb[0] <= maxPoint.x;
    bool is_pt_in_y_range = minPoint.y <= query_point_obb[1] && query_point_obb[1] <= maxPoint.y;
    bool is_pt_in_z_range = minPoint.z <= query_point_obb[2] && query_point_obb[2] <= maxPoint.z;



    //// TODO: COM과 추출된 Bounding box 내의 점들 사이의 모멘트를 계산하여 합 모멘트가 0에 근접한 경우를 안정한 경우로 판별
    //// TODO: COM과 추출된 Bounding box 내의 점들 사이의 모멘트를 계산하여 합 모멘트가 0에 근접한 경우를 안정한 경우로 판별
    // z축 높이는 무시
    bool b_plot_tmp = false;
    if(is_pt_in_x_range && is_pt_in_y_range && is_pt_in_z_range) 
    {
        // //// TODO: COM과 추출된 Bounding box 내의 점들 사이의 모멘트를 계산하여 합 모멘트가 0에 근접한 경우를 안정한 경우로 판별
        // Eigen::Vector3f net_moment; // Mx, My, Mz
        // if(0) calNetMoment(*cloudPointsProjected, query_point_obb.segment<3>(0), net_moment); // obb
        // else calNetMoment(cloud_in, query_point_raw, net_moment); // global frame
        
        // printf("\n\n");
        // m_math.printVector3f(net_moment, "net_moment");
        // printf("\n\n");
        // float thre_net_moment = 0.1;
        // if(fabs(net_moment[0]) < thre_net_moment && fabs(net_moment[1]) < thre_net_moment && fabs(net_moment[2]) < thre_net_moment)
        // {
        //     is_point_inside_obb = true;
        //     b_plot_tmp = true;
        // }

        is_point_inside_obb = true;
        b_plot_tmp = false;
    }
    else 
    {
        is_point_inside_obb = false;
        b_plot_tmp = false;
    }

    // if(b_plot) // plot
    if(b_plot_tmp) // plot
    {
        pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZRGBNormal>::Ptr cloud_plot(new pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZRGBNormal>);
        pcl::copyPointCloud(cloud_in, *cloud_plot);


        pcl::getMinMax3D(*cloud_plot, minPoint, maxPoint);
        Eigen::Matrix4f T_trans_z = Eigen::Matrix4f::Identity();
        // T_trans_z(2, 3) = -(query_point_xy_plane[2] - minPoint.z); // dz
        Eigen::Vector4f query_point_raw_plot(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 1.0);
        query_point_raw_plot.segment<3>(0) = query_point_raw;
        query_point_raw_plot = T_trans_z*query_point_raw_plot;


        pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZRGBNormal>::Ptr cloud_query_point_xy_plane(new pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZRGBNormal>);
        cloud_query_point_xy_plane->resize(1);
        cloud_query_point_xy_plane->points[0].x = query_point_raw_plot[0];
        cloud_query_point_xy_plane->points[0].y = query_point_raw_plot[1];
        cloud_query_point_xy_plane->points[0].z = query_point_raw_plot[2];

        pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZRGBNormal>::Ptr cloud_query_point_obb(new pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZRGBNormal>);
        cloud_query_point_obb->resize(1);
        cloud_query_point_obb->points[0].x = query_point_obb[0];
        cloud_query_point_obb->points[0].y = query_point_obb[1];
        cloud_query_point_obb->points[0].z = query_point_obb[2];

        pcl::visualization::PCLVisualizer viewer;
        pcl::visualization::PointCloudColorHandlerCustom<pcl::PointXYZRGBNormal> handler_1(cloud_plot, 0, 0, 255);	
        pcl::visualization::PointCloudColorHandlerCustom<pcl::PointXYZRGBNormal> handler_2(cloudPointsProjected, 255, 0, 0);	
        pcl::visualization::PointCloudColorHandlerCustom<pcl::PointXYZRGBNormal> handler_3(cloud_query_point_xy_plane, 0, 255, 0);	
        pcl::visualization::PointCloudColorHandlerCustom<pcl::PointXYZRGBNormal> handler_4(cloud_query_point_obb, 125, 125, 0);	
        
        viewer.addPointCloud(cloud_plot, handler_1, "cloud1");
        viewer.addPointCloud(cloudPointsProjected, handler_2, "cloud2");
        viewer.addPointCloud(cloud_query_point_xy_plane, handler_3, "cloud3");
        viewer.addPointCloud(cloud_query_point_obb, handler_4, "cloud4");
        viewer.setPointCloudRenderingProperties(pcl::visualization::PCL_VISUALIZER_POINT_SIZE, 2, "cloud1");
        viewer.setPointCloudRenderingProperties(pcl::visualization::PCL_VISUALIZER_POINT_SIZE, 2, "cloud2");
        viewer.setPointCloudRenderingProperties(pcl::visualization::PCL_VISUALIZER_POINT_SIZE, 10, "cloud3");
        viewer.setPointCloudRenderingProperties(pcl::visualization::PCL_VISUALIZER_POINT_SIZE, 10, "cloud4");
        // const Eigen::Quaternionf bboxQ(keep_Z_Rot);
        // const Eigen::Vector3f    bboxT(transform3.translation()); 
        viewer.addCube(bboxTransform, bboxQuaternion, box_dim(0), box_dim(1), box_dim(2), "bbox");
        viewer.setShapeRenderingProperties(pcl::visualization::PCL_VISUALIZER_REPRESENTATION, pcl::visualization::PCL_VISUALIZER_REPRESENTATION_WIREFRAME, "bbox");
        viewer.setShapeRenderingProperties(pcl::visualization::PCL_VISUALIZER_COLOR, 1.0, 0.0, 0.0, "bbox");
        viewer.addCoordinateSystem(1.0);
        viewer.setBackgroundColor(1, 1, 1);
        viewer.spin();
    }

    return is_point_inside_obb;
}

void TEMPLATE_MATCHING::calNetMoment(const pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZRGBNormal> &cloud_in, const Eigen::Vector3f &center_of_mass, Eigen::Vector3f &net_moment)
{
    // //// COM을 원점으로 좌표변환
    // pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZRGBNormal>::Ptr cloud_COM_origin(new pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZRGBNormal>);
    // Eigen::Matrix4f T = Eigen::Matrix4f::Identity();
    // T.block<3, 1>(0, 3) = -center_of_mass;
    // pcl::transformPointCloudWithNormals(cloud_in, *cloud_COM_origin, T);

    Eigen::Vector3f pt_now;
    Eigen::Vector3f vec_moment_arm;
    float mass = 1.0;
    Eigen::Vector3f F(0.0, 0.0, -9.81*mass); // 일단 중력으로 가정
    net_moment = Eigen::Vector3f::Zero();
    float sign_x = 0.0;
    float sign_y = 0.0;
    float sign_z = 0.0;
    for (size_t i = 0; i < cloud_in.size(); i++)
    {
        pt_now = cloud_in.points[i].getVector3fMap();

        // moment arm vector (r), From COM to a point in cloud
        vec_moment_arm = 0.001*(pt_now - center_of_mass); // [m]
        Eigen::Vector3f vec_xy_moment_arm(vec_moment_arm[0], vec_moment_arm[1], 0.0) ;
        Eigen::Vector3f vec_yz_moment_arm(0.0, vec_moment_arm[1], vec_moment_arm[2]) ;
        Eigen::Vector3f vec_zx_moment_arm(vec_moment_arm[0], 0.0, vec_moment_arm[2]) ;

        Eigen::Vector3f F_xy_moment_arm(F[0], F[1], 0.0) ; // Mz
        Eigen::Vector3f F_yz_moment_arm(0.0, F[1], F[2]) ; // Mx
        Eigen::Vector3f F_zx_moment_arm(F[0], 0.0, F[2]) ; // My

        Eigen::Vector3f Mx = vec_yz_moment_arm.cross(F_yz_moment_arm);
        Eigen::Vector3f My = vec_zx_moment_arm.cross(F_zx_moment_arm);
        Eigen::Vector3f Mz = vec_xy_moment_arm.cross(F_xy_moment_arm);

        // 외적의 크기 --> 모멘트
        sign_x = m_math.getVecSign(Eigen::Vector3f::UnitX(), Mx);
        sign_y = m_math.getVecSign(Eigen::Vector3f::UnitY(), My);
        sign_z = m_math.getVecSign(Eigen::Vector3f::UnitZ(), Mz);

        net_moment[0] += sign_x*Mx.norm();
        net_moment[1] += sign_y*My.norm();
        net_moment[2] += sign_z*Mz.norm();
    }
}

void TEMPLATE_MATCHING::initializeSimulationOctoMap(CTARGET_OBJECT_DATA* &target_object_data)
{
    //// 시뮬레이션에 사용되는 물체의 Octomap 초기화 (물체가 놓일 때마다 점군 데이터가 map에 추가됨)
    m_pcl_proc.initOctomapPtrWithSize(target_object_data->m_OctoMap_simulation_process, target_object_data->map_voxel_length);    

    ///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
    //// Contact normal 탐색에 사용되는 KDTree 초기화
    pcl::copyPointCloud(*target_object_data->cloud_bin_CAD_uniformly_downsampled_bin_frame_with_normal, *target_object_data->cloud_simulation_merged_object_with_bin);
    //// Bin 점군과 새로 추가된 물체의 점군을 병합한 후, KDTree 모델 생성 --> 접촉 시 contact normal 계산 시에 사용됨
    // kd tree model --> 현재까지 merge된 cloud를 다시 입력
    //// TODO: 추후 연산량 측면에서 아래 부분은 변경할 필요
    pcl::KdTreeFLANN<pcl::PointXYZ, flann::L2_Simple<float>> md_KdTree_octoMap_CAD;
    pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZ>::Ptr cloud_merged(new pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZ>);
    pcl::copyPointCloud(*target_object_data->cloud_simulation_merged_object_with_bin, *cloud_merged);
    md_KdTree_octoMap_CAD.setInputCloud(cloud_merged->makeShared());
    target_object_data->md_KdTree_octoMap_objects_with_bin_simulation_process = md_KdTree_octoMap_CAD;
    ///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
}

void TEMPLATE_MATCHING::insertPointSimulationOctoMap(CTARGET_OBJECT_DATA* &target_object_data)
{
    octomap::point3d origin(0.0f, 0.0f, 0.0f);
    octomap::Pointcloud pt_cloud_CAD;
    octomap::point3d pt_tmp(0.0f, 0.0f, 0.0f);

    for (unsigned i = 0; i < target_object_data->cloud_process_object_CAD_simulation->size(); i++)
    {
        pt_tmp(0) = target_object_data->cloud_process_object_CAD_simulation->points[i].x;
        pt_tmp(1) = target_object_data->cloud_process_object_CAD_simulation->points[i].y;
        pt_tmp(2) = target_object_data->cloud_process_object_CAD_simulation->points[i].z;
        pt_cloud_CAD.push_back(pt_tmp);
    }
    double maxRange = 2000.0; // 2000.0mm, 최대 거리 범위(센서의 주사 거리보다 더 크게 설정)
    target_object_data->m_OctoMap_simulation_process->insertPointCloud(pt_cloud_CAD, origin, maxRange); // input pointcloud, sensor origin 

    ///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
    //// Bin 점군과 새로 추가된 물체의 점군을 병합한 후, KDTree 모델 생성 --> 접촉 시 contact normal 계산 시에 사용됨
    // kd tree model --> 현재까지 merge된 cloud를 다시 입력
    //// TODO: 추후 연산량 측면에서 아래 부분은 변경할 필요
    pcl::KdTreeFLANN<pcl::PointXYZ, flann::L2_Simple<float>> md_KdTree_octoMap_CAD;
    pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZ>::Ptr cloud_merged(new pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZ>);
    pcl::copyPointCloud(*target_object_data->cloud_simulation_merged_object_with_bin, *cloud_merged);
    md_KdTree_octoMap_CAD.setInputCloud(cloud_merged->makeShared());
    target_object_data->md_KdTree_octoMap_objects_with_bin_simulation_process = md_KdTree_octoMap_CAD;
    ///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
}

